# Text files always use LF, matching Prettier's endOfLine default — otherwise
# fresh checkouts on Windows (core.autocrlf=true) materialize CRLF and the next
# `npm run format` rewrites every file, flooding git status with phantom changes.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never eol-convert
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.ttf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
